Document: ImageFormatLoaderExtension
Path: godot/classes/class_imageformatloaderextension.rst
Summary: Extends Godot's image format support by implementing custom loaders.

The engine supports multiple image formats out of the box (PNG, SVG, JPEG, WebP to name a few), but you can choose to implement support for additional image formats by extending this class. Be sure to respect the documented return types and values. You should create an instance of it, and call add_format_loader() to register that loader during the initialization phase. Note: Proper implementation requires adherence to specified return types and values for compatibility.
